[assistant]   "summary": "Hibernate Validator 9.1.0.Final needs a Jakarta Expression Language implementation for normal Java SE validation coverage; the artifact only provides/declares the EL API as optional/provided, while the reference documentation says an EL implementation must be added outside a Jakarta EE container.",
